| Event hooks | auto-commit-on-exit, custom-compaction, git-checkpoint |
| UI customization | custom-header, custom-footer, built-in-tool-renderer |
| Session lifecycle | confirm-destructive, dirty-repo-guard |
| Inter-extension comms | event-bus |
| External integration | file-trigger |
| Command registration | bookmark, commands, dynamic-tools |
